http://wpf.codeplex.com/workitem/list/basic?field=CreationDate&direction=Descending&issuesToDisplay=Open&keywords=accordion&emailSubscribedItemsOnly=false
 
This lead to a Infinite Loop which was caused in the OnSelectedItemPropertyChanged event, when IsValidItemForSelection is checked.
 
if (!source.IsValidItemForSelection(newValue))
            {
                // reset to oldvalue
                source._selectedItemNestedLevel++;

                /**
                *Author: Jason Mogera
