                *Added Commented the bottom line out for it will cause a infinite loop.
                *THe Accordian control doesn't work when the DataSOurce is changed dynamically. * 
                **/              

                //source.SetValue(SelectedItemProperty, oldValue);
                source._selectedItemNestedLevel--;
            }
 
This got my application running without the infinite loop, but now I am getting a behavior where the once an AccordionItem is collapsed, it doesn't expand anymore.
 
